[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/64/6497.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1328556","time":"2018-3-18 02:52","userId":"magicfish1990","userName":"铃猫 一边吃🥗一边","userSign":"","message":"GPT是文件系统<br>GRUB是引导器<br>refind是引导器<br>EFI是主板上的系统<br><br>所以你在问什么<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/98/179870.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1328559","time":"2018-3-18 03:14","userId":"open4all","userName":"Lrolic.holic","userSign":"","message":"嗯，具体是想问set root这个是怎么用的，和加载非eif文件所引导的Linux怎么手动引导(比如kernel xxx这几个指令怎么用)还有衍生出来的引导器的工作原理(引导器就是一个图形化的shell上的批处理还是本身是个被编译的efi程序...)(又说多了，我对这些事是懵逼的也不知道咋提问)"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/64/6497.jpg","floor":"#2-2","id":"1328562","time":"2018-3-18 03:31","userId":"magicfish1990","userName":"铃猫 一边吃🥗一边","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Lrolic.holic</span> 说: 嗯，具体是想问set root这个是怎么用的，和加载非eif文件所引导的Linux怎么手动引导(比如kernel xxx这几个指令怎么用)还有衍生出来的引导器的工作原理(引导器就是一个图形化的shel...</q></div>set root 是指定启动程序所在分区 set root='hd0,gpt2'<br>linux 内核路径 参数<br>initrd 内存镜像路径<br><br>引导器本身是汇编"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/98/179870.jpg","floor":"#2-3","id":"1328614","time":"2018-3-18 09:54","userId":"open4all","userName":"Lrolic.holic","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">MagicFish1990一边吃草一边</span> 说: set root 是指定启动程序所在分区 set root='hd0,gpt2'<br>linux 内核路径 参数<br>initrd 内存镜像路径<br><br>引导器本身是汇编</q></div>引导器原来是汇编大佬。。。怪不得找不到efi编辑器<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">easyuefi所编辑的东西是个{文件}还是{mbr(类似)分区表}还是{bios}。。。这应该是最后的问题了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/68/286878.jpg","floor":"#2-4","id":"1328960","time":"2018-3-19 00:39","userId":"yejingchen","userName":"菜叶","userSign":"","message":"GPT 是分区表不是文件系统"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/64/6497.jpg","floor":"#2-5","id":"1328992","time":"2018-3-19 04:32","userId":"magicfish1990","userName":"铃猫 一边吃🥗一边","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">菜叶</span> 说: GPT 是分区表不是文件系统</q></div>脑抽<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/64/6497.jpg","floor":"#2-6","id":"1328993","time":"2018-3-19 04:34","userId":"magicfish1990","userName":"铃猫 一边吃🥗一边","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Lrolic.holic</span> 说: 引导器原来是汇编大佬。。。怪不得找不到efi编辑器easyuefi所编辑的东西是个{文件}还是{mbr(类似)分区表}还是{bios}。。。这应该是最后的问题了</q></div>UEFI分成2部分，一部分保存在BIOS里的参数（一般是默认引导文件，可选），另一部分是EFI分区里的文件。<br>所以它大概两个都编辑<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#2-7","id":"1329024","time":"2018-3-19 09:37","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Lrolic.holic</span> 说: 引导器原来是汇编大佬。。。怪不得找不到efi编辑器easyuefi所编辑的东西是个{文件}还是{mbr(类似)分区表}还是{bios}。。。这应该是最后的问题了</q></div>我一般是用efibootmgr来捣鼓UEFI的启动项<br>bcd和grub2都是装载/boot/efi/EFI/里的（这其实就是那个efi分区）<br>UEFI启动时候会找到第一个EFI分区，然后就读里面的文件夹<br>我一般不用grub4dos的"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/08/290840.jpg","floor":"#2-8","id":"1331239","time":"2018-3-25 12:28","userId":"nasa33","userName":"Userbot","userSign":"","message":"200円一次"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/64/6497.jpg","floor":"#2-9","id":"1331270","time":"2018-3-25 14:44","userId":"magicfish1990","userName":"铃猫 一边吃🥗一边","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">NASA</span> 说: 200円一次</q></div>先来一万円的<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/85.gif\" smileid=\"124\" alt=\"(bgm108)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/74/37469.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1328931","time":"2018-3-19 00:02","userId":"fantasy","userName":"fantasy","userSign":"(Q, Σ, Γ, δ, q0, Z0, F)","message":"在surface 上装linux吗？","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/98/179870.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1329829","time":"2018-3-21 09:39","userId":"open4all","userName":"Lrolic.holic","userSign":"","message":"linux自动安装的那个镜像不起作用，不知道是不是个例"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/74/37469.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1329867","time":"2018-3-21 12:13","userId":"fantasy","userName":"fantasy","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Lrolic.holic</span> 说: linux自动安装的那个镜像不起作用，不知道是不是个例</q></div>自动安装？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/98/179870.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1330770","time":"2018-3-23 15:46","userId":"open4all","userName":"Lrolic.holic","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">fantasy</span> 说: 自动安装？</q></div>做成镜像自己安装的那个"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/59/55968.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1329007","time":"2018-3-19 08:29","userId":"zodiacg","userName":"zodiacg","userSign":"(那谁谁家那小谁)","message":"不同的bootloader的语法当然是不一样的……只是长得像而已……<br>uefi我就没用过grub了……现在用的是systemd-boot……","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/98/179870.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1329830","time":"2018-3-21 09:42","userId":"open4all","userName":"Lrolic.holic","userSign":"","message":"长得像可以用，撸好了先用着。。等换电脑。。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1329023","time":"2018-3-19 09:37","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"(媛娇系是检验大法的唯一标准)","message":"现在grub还在用吗？","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1329025","time":"2018-3-19 09:41","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"大部分distro的默认安装还是会装上grub的，毕竟grub有shim，不需要关闭secureboot，否则你得手工导入那个发行版的公钥了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#5-2","id":"1329048","time":"2018-3-19 10:32","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">LunarShaddow</span> 说: 大部分distro的默认安装还是会装上grub的，毕竟grub有shim，不需要关闭secureboot，否则你得手工导入那个发行版的公钥了</q></div>我一般都是去关掉的<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">，不过苏菲似乎关不掉？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#5-3","id":"1329123","time":"2018-3-19 15:09","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">lhb5883-污喵王VIP⑩</span> 说: 我一般都是去关掉的，不过苏菲似乎关不掉？</q></div>嘛，发行版都是为了最大兼容性考虑啦<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/01.gif\" smileid=\"40\" alt=\"(bgm24)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/98/179870.jpg","floor":"#5-4","id":"1329831","time":"2018-3-21 09:43","userId":"open4all","userName":"Lrolic.holic","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">lhb5883-污喵王VIP⑩</span> 说: 我一般都是去关掉的，不过苏菲似乎关不掉？</q></div>苏菲可以关，只是开机背景变成红色。。慎得慌<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#5-5","id":"1329842","time":"2018-3-21 10:06","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Lrolic.holic</span> 说: 苏菲可以关，只是开机背景变成红色。。慎得慌</q></div>想起来了,是没有CSM启动,只能UEFI Boot<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1329029","time":"2018-3-19 09:56","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"(Death is the gateway to Eternity, my dear.)","message":"从我的知识来看，<br>1. /EFI/BOOT/bootx64.efi是默认的引导器（它是什么都可能），当主板NVRAM里啥条目都没写的时候使用；微软的BCD在/EFI/MICROSOFT/BOOT/BCD里<br>2. 启动条目信息存在主板NVRAM里，有一次我的主板发抽根本保存不了EFI引导项，重刷固件刷好的；如果主板没有写，有时会扫描EFI分区<br>3. refind和winbcd和grub（或它的shim）是同一个层级，都是引导器<br>4.1. initrd是initial ram disk的简称，在kernel载入的同时载入到内存里，代替你真正的/提供驱动（因为很有可能你的root partition通过iscsi/pxe/奇怪的设备载入，驱动如果在奇怪的设备上，那不就死循环了）；如果你是量身定制的系统（Gentoo/LFS），可以直接把本机要用的驱动编译到kernel里，就不用initrd了；但是发行版如果把所有驱动打进去，内核就太大了……<br>4.2. 有关语法，请RTFM <a href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/grub/manual/grub/grub.html#Multi_002dboot-manual-config\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://www.gnu.org/software/gru ... dboot-manual-config</a><br>5. 通常来说，请不要信中文书，尽量看原文（或译作）；教材的时效性实在是不敢恭维（比如谭浩强）<br>PS. 如果想弄懂系统启动原理，可以尝试自己编译一个LFS出来，当然，不要用寨板，请用PC","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/98/179870.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1329832","time":"2018-3-21 09:45","userId":"open4all","userName":"Lrolic.holic","userSign":"","message":"谢谢谢谢，走心的解答；过几天我给我的新本子设置好回来就研究这些<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/68/286878.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1329844","time":"2018-3-21 10:25","userId":"yejingchen","userName":"菜叶","userSign":"(你的爱还不够啊！)","message":"从来都是 refind 自动发现启动项的路过<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"> menuentry 写不来的","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/15/341586.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1331225","time":"2018-3-25 11:37","userId":"joenahm","userName":"张弗若","userSign":"(考前记一记，喝前摇一摇)","message":"所以楼主的问题解决了吗","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/78/257815.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1331228","time":"2018-3-25 11:42","userId":"yanshe","userName":"九八式衍射弹","userSign":"","message":"Surface Pro3 i5版 装linux好用不？下学期得上计算机系统课，估计要被强装linux了","sub":[]}]